('Spanish Writing Center Tutoring Hours', 'Center for Latino Heritage & Spanish Language Excellence', 'Our Spanish Writing Center at CLaSE (Center for Latino heritage and Spanish language Excellence) is now offering  more  tutoring hours online and in-person starting  February 3rd . Our amazing tutors are Lorena Tacle and Ivan Podobed. If you need to improve you writing skills in Spanish, polish your written structures, or get help with your paper, article, letter, etc. check our tutors availability and book an appointment in our website https://www.montclair.edu/clase/our-initiatives/spanish-writing-center/', '2025-02-03 17:00:00', '2025-02-03 19:00:00', 1645, 'Online'),
